race.comment: LADY JULIA (5) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (22.25) at this track in a Free For All over 390m. Can measure up this time. LAURISTON GIRL (8) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 1.5 lengths (21.94) at this track. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. FEDERAL PLAYER (7) has a superb record at the course, unbeaten so far from three starts. Recorded a neck win (22.35) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. BRING YOUR BEST (2) placed last start and is in the mix again.
